{"tid":242754,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加冷對「空襲」：我唔受有錢人影響","createTime":"2017-05-14T07:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T17:07:35.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d18bf1676a978bc9867dfb614c596db3b46ed50b","tid":242754,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T07:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/8/278/18035619278/18046962851_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F8%2F278%2F18035619278%2F18046962851_600x399.jpg&h=c193babf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3f%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=00f8a759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴周末大勝史篤城之戰，一張要求他下台的標語在空中飄揚，雲加冷對這個衝著自己的行為。<br />\n<br />\n比賽期間，一幅寫上&quot;Wenger - Out Means Out&quot;字句的橫額在球場上空飄揚。被問到已不止一次受到球迷「空襲」，雲加處之泰然：「當你說球迷，你所指是甚麼？那些富有的？」<br />\n<br />\n「看！我受聘為我喜愛的球會工作，而我會盡心盡力作出貢獻。我不會受此影響，我所做的就是盡自己的努力。」這位法國名帥續說：「今天我們有69分，盼於周二有72分，之後我會為球會傾盡全力。」<br />\n<br />\n對於別人批評，他顯得滿不在乎：「我想集中在足球，其餘都沒那麼重要。我不是政客，我身處運動界，我愛運動，一天為我所愛付出24小時。我的工作是公開的，有人同意，有些人不同意。」"},{"pid":"fa4430c871152c6d4b39a34505367d0619fcc068","tid":242754,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T09:08:09.000Z","msg":"走啦死老野！"},{"pid":"37b2f72c3434486b126fd60b739594baa51da53e","tid":242754,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T09:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>走啦死老野！</blockquote><br />\n場都冇得出就收皮la"},{"pid":"f4d41e0bca780e7c238005523780ec067a0d2f32","tid":242754,"uid":106483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T09:09:26.000Z","msg":"今次有冇香港球迷夾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，支持爺爺入前四入佢地皮"},{"pid":"447954c0576ac652491b34c5615261ee3a669352","tid":242754,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T09:10:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>走啦死老野！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1920c54118331e6945cf033a53d8ca2362427d4","tid":242754,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>走啦死老野！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反雲狗去死"}]}